        <description>&lt;p&gt;5天了才送到，好慢！！！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;盒子本身挺重的，据说里面加了铁块ORZ。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-2.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-2358&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-2.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;xiaomi-box-2&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;960&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-2.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-2-150x112.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-2-300x225.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-2-1024x768.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;买完才发现原来遥控器操作比我想象中的糟糕多了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;键盘是生产力，触摸屏是玩具，遥控器可以杀人。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;输入密码花了我半天。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最重要的是，竟然连Bilibili都看不了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;OMG遥控根本选择不了啊！！！&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-3.jpg&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-full wp-image-2359&#34; src=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-3.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;xiaomi-box-3&#34; width=&#34;1280&#34; height=&#34;907&#34; srcset=&#34;https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-3.jpg 1280w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-3-150x106.jpg 150w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-3-300x212.jpg 300w, https://umi.im/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/xiaomi-box-3-1024x725.jpg 1024w&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后用泰捷TV搜，竟然只更新到了第二话。_(:3ゝ∠)_&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最后只能用MIRACAST把手机屏幕投射到电视上。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;据说可以用OTG线连接鼠标，刚拍了一条。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HTPC大法好。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;有钱最好直接上HTPC，免得各种折腾。&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
